            <h3>Frequently Asked Questions</h3>

            <p><strong>1. What is the delivery time?</strong></p>
            <p>We deliver within 2 to 5 days nationwide using Viettel Post. For immediate delivery within Ho Chi Minh City, we offer expedited courier service. Please call our hotline at 0903088038 for assistance.</p>

            <p><strong>2. Does CD Station offer Cash on Delivery (COD) service?</strong></p>
            <p>COD service is available only for existing customers and excludes products under pre-order. Customers need to pay 100% of the order value, including shipping costs. Upon receipt of payment, you will receive a confirmation email within 24 hours. For existing customers, please contact us via Facebook to arrange for COD.</p>

            <p><strong>3. How can I contact customer support regarding my order?</strong></p>
            <p>You can reach our sales support team via email at <a href="" style="color: #50222b">CDStation@gmail.com</a>.</p>

            <p><strong>4. What are your operating hours?</strong></p>
            <p>CD Station is open from 10 AM to 8 PM daily.</p>

            <p><strong>5. How can I order products that are out of stock or merchandise from international artist websites?</strong></p>
            <p>Please message us on our Facebook fan page for assistance and pricing. CD Station will place orders for available products. Shipping time from the US/UK to Vietnam ranges from 2 to 4 weeks.</p>

            <p><strong>6. Does CD Station reissue limited edition box sets?</strong></p>
            <p>All limited edition (limited version) products released by CD Station are not reissued. We appreciate your continued support for our artist's products.</p>

            <p><strong>7. Does CD Station sell counterfeit discs?</strong></p>
            <p>CD Station exclusively sells authentic products alongside production releases. All products sold at CD Station are authentic.</p>
